<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Factory 3D</title>
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">

  <style>
      body {
          margin: 0;
          overflow: hidden;
          font-family: Inter, Arial, sans-serif;
          background: #181b22;
      }

      #scene-container {
          width: 100vw;
          height: 100vh;
      }

      .machine-card {
          position: fixed;
          top: 24px;
          right: 24px;
          width: min(380px, calc(100vw - 48px));
          padding: 18px 18px 16px;
          border-radius: 18px;
          background: rgba(12, 16, 22, 0.84);
          border: 1px solid rgba(255, 138, 0, 0.18);
          box-shadow: 0 18px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.38);
          backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
          color: #f3f7ff;
          z-index: 20;
          display: none;
      }

      .machine-card.is-visible {
          display: block;
      }

      .machine-card__close {
          position: absolute;
          top: 10px;
          right: 10px;
          width: 32px;
          height: 32px;
          border: 0;
          border-radius: 999px;
          background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
          color: #fff;
          cursor: pointer;
          font-size: 20px;
          line-height: 32px;
      }

      .machine-card__tag {
          display: inline-block;
          margin-bottom: 10px;
          padding: 6px 10px;
          border-radius: 999px;
          font-size: 12px;
          letter-spacing: 0.04em;
          text-transform: uppercase;
          color: #ffb15d;
          background: rgba(255, 138, 0, 0.08);
          border: 1px solid rgba(255, 138, 0, 0.16);
      }

      .machine-card__title {
          margin: 0 0 8px;
          font-size: 22px;
          line-height: 1.15;
      }

      .machine-card__status {
          display: inline-block;
          margin-bottom: 12px;
          padding: 5px 10px;
          border-radius: 999px;
          font-size: 13px;
          background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
          color: #d9e6ff;
      }

      .machine-card__desc {
          margin: 0;
          font-size: 14px;
          line-height: 1.55;
          color: #d1d8e3;
      }

      .machine-card__meta {
          margin-top: 12px;
          font-size: 12px;
          color: #8e9bb0;
      }

      .machine-card.is-active {
          border-color: rgba(0, 255, 170, 0.32);
      }

      .machine-card.is-service {
          border-color: rgba(255, 195, 0, 0.32);
      }

      .machine-card.is-off {
          border-color: rgba(255, 92, 92, 0.32);
      }

      .warehouse-card {
          width: min(560px, calc(100vw - 48px));
          max-height: calc(100vh - 48px);
          overflow: auto;
      }

      .warehouse-content {
          margin-top: 8px;
          display: flex;
          flex-direction: column;
          gap: 14px;
      }

      .warehouse-group__title {
          margin: 0 0 8px;
          font-size: 14px;
          color: #ffb15d;
          text-transform: uppercase;
          letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      }

      .warehouse-list {
          list-style: none;
          padding: 0;
          margin: 0;
          display: flex;
          flex-direction: column;
          gap: 10px;
      }

      .warehouse-item {
          display: flex;
          justify-content: space-between;
          gap: 14px;
          padding: 10px 12px;
          border-radius: 12px;
          background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
          border: 1px solid rgba(255, 138, 0, 0.12);
      }

      .warehouse-item__content {
          flex: 1;
          min-width: 0;
      }

      .warehouse-item__name {
          font-weight: 600;
          margin-bottom: 4px;
      }

      .warehouse-item__meta {
          font-size: 12px;
          color: #ffb15d;
          margin-bottom: 4px;
      }

      .warehouse-item__desc {
          font-size: 13px;
          line-height: 1.45;
          color: #d1d8e3;
      }

      .warehouse-item__actions {
          display: flex;
          align-items: center;
      }

      .warehouse-item__take {
          align-self: center;
          border: 1px solid rgba(255, 138, 0, 0.28);
          background: rgba(255, 138, 0, 0.12);
          color: #ffb15d;
          border-radius: 999px;
          padding: 8px 12px;
          cursor: pointer;
          white-space: nowrap;
          transition: transform 0.15s ease, background 0.15s ease, opacity 0.15s ease;
      }

      .warehouse-item__take:hover {
          transform: translateY(-1px);
          background: rgba(255, 138, 0, 0.2);
      }

      .warehouse-item__take:disabled {
          opacity: 0.55;
          cursor: wait;
      }
      .confirm-modal {
          position: fixed;
          inset: 0;
          display: none;
          z-index: 50;
      }

      .confirm-modal.is-visible {
          display: block;
      }

      .confirm-modal__backdrop {
          position: absolute;
          inset: 0;
          background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55);
          backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
      }

      .confirm-modal__panel {
          position: absolute;
          top: 50%;
          left: 50%;
          transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
          width: min(420px, calc(100vw - 32px));
          padding: 20px;
          border-radius: 18px;
          background: rgba(12, 16, 22, 0.92);
          border: 1px solid rgba(255, 138, 0, 0.2);
          box-shadow: 0 18px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45);
          color: #f3f7ff;
      }

      .confirm-modal__tag {
          display: inline-block;
          margin-bottom: 10px;
          padding: 6px 10px;
          border-radius: 999px;
          font-size: 12px;
          text-transform: uppercase;
          letter-spacing: 0.04em;
          color: #ffb15d;
          background: rgba(255, 138, 0, 0.08);
          border: 1px solid rgba(255, 138, 0, 0.16);
      }

      .confirm-modal__title {
          margin: 0 0 10px;
          font-size: 20px;
      }

      .confirm-modal__text {
          margin: 0 0 18px;
          font-size: 14px;
          line-height: 1.55;
          color: #d1d8e3;
      }

      .confirm-modal__actions {
          display: flex;
          justify-content: flex-end;
          gap: 10px;
      }

      .confirm-modal__btn {
          border-radius: 999px;
          padding: 9px 14px;
          border: 1px solid transparent;
          cursor: pointer;
          font-size: 14px;
      }

      .confirm-modal__btn--ghost {
          background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
          color: #f3f7ff;
          border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      }

      .confirm-modal__btn--primary {
          background: rgba(255, 138, 0, 0.18);
          color: #ffb15d;
          border-color: rgba(255, 138, 0, 0.28);
      }
      .user-badge {
          position: fixed;
          top: 24px;
          left: 24px;
          z-index: 40;
          padding: 10px 14px;
          border-radius: 999px;
          background: rgba(12, 16, 22, 0.84);
          border: 1px solid rgba(255, 138, 0, 0.18);
          color: #f3f7ff;
          backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
          box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.28);
          display: flex;
          gap: 8px;
          align-items: center;
          font-size: 14px;
      }

      .user-badge__label {
          color: #8e9bb0;
      }

      .user-badge__name {
          color: #ffb15d;
          font-weight: 600;
      }

      .profile-modal {
          position: fixed;
          inset: 0;
          display: none;
          z-index: 60;
      }

      .profile-modal.is-visible {
          display: block;
      }

      .profile-modal__backdrop {
          position: absolute;
          inset: 0;
          background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
          backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
      }

      .profile-modal__panel {
          position: absolute;
          top: 50%;
          left: 50%;
          transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
          width: min(420px, calc(100vw - 32px));
          padding: 20px;
          border-radius: 18px;
          background: rgba(12, 16, 22, 0.94);
          border: 1px solid rgba(255, 138, 0, 0.2);
          box-shadow: 0 18px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45);
          color: #f3f7ff;
      }

      .profile-modal__tag {
          display: inline-block;
          margin-bottom: 10px;
          padding: 6px 10px;
          border-radius: 999px;
          font-size: 12px;
          text-transform: uppercase;
          letter-spacing: 0.04em;
          color: #ffb15d;
          background: rgba(255, 138, 0, 0.08);
          border: 1px solid rgba(255, 138, 0, 0.16);
      }

      .profile-modal__title {
          margin: 0 0 10px;
          font-size: 20px;
      }

      .profile-modal__text {
          margin: 0 0 16px;
          font-size: 14px;
          line-height: 1.55;
          color: #d1d8e3;
      }

      .profile-modal__input {
          width: 100%;
          box-sizing: border-box;
          padding: 12px 14px;
          border-radius: 12px;
          border: 1px solid rgba(255, 138, 0, 0.18);
          background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
          color: #f3f7ff;
          outline: none;
          font-size: 14px;
      }

      .profile-modal__input:focus {
          border-color: rgba(255, 138, 0, 0.36);
      }

      .profile-modal__actions {
          margin-top: 16px;
          display: flex;
          justify-content: flex-end;
      }

      .profile-modal__btn {
          border-radius: 999px;
          padding: 10px 14px;
          border: 1px solid transparent;
          cursor: pointer;
          font-size: 14px;
      }

      .profile-modal__btn--primary {
          background: rgba(255, 138, 0, 0.18);
          color: #ffb15d;
          border-color: rgba(255, 138, 0, 0.28);
      }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
<div id="scene-container"></div>

<div id="machine-card" class="machine-card">
  <button class="machine-card__close" id="machine-card-close" aria-label="Закрыть">×</button>
  <div class="machine-card__tag">Станок</div>
  <h3 class="machine-card__title">Выбери модель</h3>
  <div class="machine-card__status">Статус: —</div>
  <p class="machine-card__desc">Наведите курсор на модель и нажмите на неё, чтобы открыть карточку.</p>
  <div class="machine-card__meta">Нажми Esc, чтобы закрыть</div>
</div>
<div id="user-badge" class="user-badge">
  <span class="user-badge__label">Пользователь:</span>
  <span id="user-badge-name" class="user-badge__name"><%= session[:user_name].presence || "Гость" %></span>
</div>

<div id="profile-modal" class="profile-modal" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="profile-modal__backdrop"></div>

  <div class="profile-modal__panel" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-labelledby="profile-title">
    <div class="profile-modal__tag">Регистрация</div>
    <h3 class="profile-modal__title" id="profile-title">Введите ваше ФИО</h3>
    <p class="profile-modal__text">Это имя будет отображаться в правом верхнем углу и записываться в журнал выдачи материалов.</p>

    <input id="profile-name" class="profile-modal__input" type="text" placeholder="Иванов Иван Иванович">

    <div class="profile-modal__actions">
      <button type="button" class="profile-modal__btn profile-modal__btn--primary" id="profile-save">
        Сохранить
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div id="confirm-modal" class="confirm-modal" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="confirm-modal__backdrop"></div>

  <div class="confirm-modal__panel" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-labelledby="confirm-title">
    <div class="confirm-modal__tag">Склад</div>
    <h3 class="confirm-modal__title" id="confirm-title">Подтвердите действие</h3>
    <p class="confirm-modal__text" id="confirm-message"></p>

    <div class="confirm-modal__actions">
      <button type="button" class="confirm-modal__btn confirm-modal__btn--ghost" id="confirm-cancel">
        Отмена
      </button>
      <button type="button" class="confirm-modal__btn confirm-modal__btn--primary" id="confirm-ok">
        Взять
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<script type="module" src="/scene.js"></script>
</body>
</html>